WorkItem.Description:
Hello Codeplex members.

I'm able to export data from database to xls file. However I'm unable to import them back to database. I'm not a php expert. So I hope anyone can help me to import the data from xls to database. Please write a simple example so that I can understand.

Thanks
WorkItem.Summary: How to Import xls to php (database)
